doc.previous: The following Air Force wing organizations flew the various C 97 models at some time during their existence 13  The Israelis turned to Stratocruisers and KC 97s when they could not buy the highly regarded C 130 citation needed They adapted Boeing 377 Stratocruiser airliners into transports including many using C 97 tail sections including the loading ramp citation needed Others were adapted with swiveling tails and refueling pods citation needed One Israeli C 97 was downed by an Egyptian SA 2 Guideline missile on 17 September 1971 while flying as an electronic counter measures platform some 12 miles from the Suez Canal 7 8
